::Zardus::

Zardus stops firing, waiting for Hurricane and Wheeljack to deal with 
this bot. In front of them, the second shuttle lands.

Zardus recieves the transmission from Composer and 
replies. "Excellent. Unload your shuttle and then fly to my 
coordinates and begin deconstructing this ship that is here. Don't 
worry about storing the material you have now, that'll be taken care 
of automatically."
